  "prompt": "What is the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai?",
  "response": "As of my last knowledge update in October 2023, the average salary for an IT consultant in Dubai varies depending on factors such as experience, qualifications, and specific skill sets. Generally, the salary range for IT consultants in Dubai can be between AED 10,000 to AED 25,000 per month. More experienced consultants or those with specialized skills may earn upwards of AED 30,000 per month.\n\nFor the most accurate and up-to-date information, it's advisable to refer to local job portals or salary surveys specific to the UAE.",
